description:
Darkness Radio presents Supernatural News/Parashare: Let's Put It To Bed Once and For All Edition!

It has been an interesting week, to say the least and there is some juicy stuff out there... so... Let's put it to bed once and for all!! As far as the paranormal stories go... what did you think we were talking about?

This week... Netflix is making a movie about the Demon House, Uri Gellar claims that an alien mass landing is coming soon, you might be trapped in the Matrix, and you don't know it! and it turns out that all seven of you out there forced Beer City Bruiser to change his profession!! Check it out in this episode!Â
